These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, subway
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, turkish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dannemann, pall-mall
1. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Transport   | subway       | motorbike     | bus    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | thai          | indian   |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | pall-mall | dannemann |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, cabbage, nectarine
3 different games are played: billiard, whist, backgammon
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, fonseca, bluemaster
1. the bluemaster-smoker is the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | avocado     | nectarine  | cabbage  |
| Game   | backgammon | whist | billiard    |
| Cigar     | dunhill      | bluemaster    | fonseca |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, kiwi, plum
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, ebony, black
City: edinburgh, hamburg, prague
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to prague is the person eating apple##1
3. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating apple##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Food          | apple         | plum     | kiwi   |
| Color   | ebony       | mauve     | black |
| City         | prague | edinburgh | hamburg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, eggplant, watermelon
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, sudoku, skydiving
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, snake
1. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Food   | asparagus | watermelon  | eggplant |
| Hobby        | skydiving | sudoku  | video-games |
| Pet        | ferret | goldfish | snake         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
House: townhouse, wooden, art-deco
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, fanta
1. the american is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the australian is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the townhouse house##1
4. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
5. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
6. the wooden house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| House   | art-deco | townhouse  | wooden  |
| Nationality   | australian  | american | chinese |
| Beverage           | soy-milk  | fanta    | milk    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, sprite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, dunhill, old-henry
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, salsa, metal
1. the person drinking cola is between the fan of metal and the old-henry-smoker##2
2. the chaman-smoker is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Beverage    | sprite  | cola  | milk        |
| Cigar       | old-henry | dunhill | chaman |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | salsa   | metal   |

