.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, sports, western
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, coach, architect
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, june, december
1. the person watching sports movies is between the paramedic and the person watching western movies##2
2. the architect is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | sports        | western |
| Job           | paramedic   | coach      | architect     |
| Birthday         | december | june | september    |

