.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, pineapple, potato
City: marseilles, boston, edinburgh
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, scooter, tram
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person eating potato##2
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the person eating potato is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the tram is the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Food    | corn   | pineapple | potato       |
| City     | edinburgh  | marseilles  | boston |
| Transport   | scooter | van  | tram       |

