.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, lacrosse
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, polish, thai
House: cottage, victorian, ranch-style
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
3. the polish is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
4. the pakistani is on the right of the polish##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the cottage house and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Sport         | skateboarding | parkour | lacrosse |
| Nationality   | thai       | polish  | pakistani     |
| House           | victorian     | ranch-style     | cottage          |

