.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, nurse, photographer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, cain, vegafina
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, october, march
1. the nurse is on the far right##1
2. the cain-smoker is the cain-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
4. the chef is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
6. the vegafina-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Job           | photographer | chef        | nurse   |
| Cigar   | cain | vegafina | fonseca    |
| Birthday   | march         | september      | october |

