There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, ivory, orange
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, scooter, skateboard
1. the person eating peach is the person who likes purple##1
2. the person eating garlic is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |    3    |
| Food         | peach | cranberry      | garlic  |
| Color         | purple         | orange      | ivory    |
| Transport   | bike         | skateboard | scooter |

