.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-12::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, banana, plum
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, daisy, marigold
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, time-travel
1. the person who growsdaisy is the person eating plum##1
2. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person eating banana is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3       |
| Food         | banana        | raspberry  | plum      |
| Flower           | marigold | aconite | daisy |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy        | family   | time-travel  |

