.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, lime, blueberry
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, april, august
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
4. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage    | 7up        | hot-chocolate | sprite     |
| Food       | broccoli | lime          | blueberry |
| Birthday   | april     | august          | march       |

