.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-14::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, artichoke, grapefruit
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, may, april
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, blue, black
1. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
2. the person who likes blue is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Food          | apple | artichoke | grapefruit |
| Birthday           | november | april   | may  |
| Color   | blue | green   | black        |

