.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, drama, martial-arts
3 different games are played: domino, whist, go
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, june
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person playing domino is the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person watching drama movies is the person playing whist##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | martial-arts | action |
| Game   | whist        | domino         | go |
| Birthday           | january | june         | september   |

