.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-16::.
City: miami, rome, boston
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, lacrosse, skiing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
6. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| City         | rome   | miami     | boston   |
| Sport           | lacrosse  | water-polo | skiing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | romance     | disaster |

