.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, pilot, social-worker
There 3 different types of food: papaya, garlic, spinach
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, country, r&b
1. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
2. the paramedic is in an even position##4
3. the social-worker is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the pilot is the person eating garlic##1
5. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Job     | pilot      | paramedic | social-worker |
| Food     | garlic | papaya      | spinach           |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | soul  | country    |

