.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-18::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, march, december
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard, rat
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, poker
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
3. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Birthday    | may | december      | march     |
| Pet         | lizard  | goldfish | rat        |
| Game   | scrabble | poker    | mah-jongg |

