The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, handball
There are 3 different nationalities: german, malaysian, polish
1. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the polish##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3      |
| Pet      | goldfish | chinchilla  | bird |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | handball    | parkour       |
| Nationality   | german   | polish | malaysian   |

