.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, sudoku
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, security-guard, musician
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, almond-milk
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the security-guard##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
4. the musician is the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the musician is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
7. the freelancer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | sudoku      | collecting | card-games |
| Job   | security-guard | freelancer      | musician    |
| Beverage           | almond-milk      | iced-tea        | soy-milk       |

 